{"tid":2311121,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"防中國危害國安 德國傳封殺中企收購衛星和無線電技術公司","createTime":"2020-12-03T23:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T06:20:14.000Z","uid":204533,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e82c4db5379530401b707943486831c609e1c08b","tid":2311121,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:03:23.000Z","msg":"德國媒體報導，總理梅克爾（Angela Merkel）政府以國安風險為由，禁止中國航天發展公司收購一家專門從事包括5G在內的衛星和無線電技術的德國公司。<br />\n<br />\n德新社（DPA）援引政府文件報導，總部位於北萊因-西發利亞邦（North Rhine-Westphalia）的IMST公司是航天發展的收購目標，而航天發展是中國國有國防集團中國航天科工集團的子公司，該公司生產軍事通訊系統。<br />\n<br />\n德國經濟部證實，梅克爾內閣2日同意阻止一家外國公司進行收購，但未透露相關公司名稱。德國外交部在一份聲明中告訴法新社：「審查標準始終是具體收購對德國公共秩序或安全構成的威脅。」<br />\n<br />\n隨著越來越多中國公司爭搶德國專有技術，對此發出的警訊也日益增加，梅克爾政府正努力加強監督非歐盟收購案。<br />\n<br />\n德國政府目前可以審查股權比例在25%或以上的收購案，不過目前未定的法律草案要求將門檻降低至10%。（中央社）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201204/LNYHKSAVS5DSNFOE6Q5AGSAXAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201204%2FLNYHKSAVS5DSNFOE6Q5AGSAXAQ%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=94f37811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201204%2FLNYHKSAVS5DSNFOE6Q5AGSAXAQ%2F&h=665bd847\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201204/LNYHKSAVS5DSNFOE6Q5AGSAXAQ/</a>"},{"pid":"20948493dd9328bec6b6ed36c528dd83f9c09894","tid":2311121,"uid":13343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa8ca035256a345ce6df5440aa66205c7206400","tid":2311121,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:49:12.000Z","msg":"聽吓先，之前都講唔準大陸收購機械人公司，最後咪又係賣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706c0861bdb671a7e7396937d1645d3c9f245848","tid":2311121,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7680c203fa103197694607af40a748b12c09f384","tid":2311121,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"Merkel都出手<br />\n<br />\n小熊維尼犯眾憎"},{"pid":"32c41699b211fc8bebafc9ead971341334c9ea88","tid":2311121,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca9f76df8c238ae32e5cde8bd686b41ff9988c9","tid":2311121,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"德國國安法，嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b2ef4fb2a94cdefc9e49af8e56c11ecbaa1c1b","tid":2311121,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"德國咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愈戰愈勇"},{"pid":"b3257691bc8c99fdc9469c36515ca4590c029d88","tid":2311121,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"又話人哋打壓佢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e16d3606c4a600bbefa00078ae1eb723e7fc654","tid":2311121,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fa8ca035256a345ce6df5440aa66205c7206400","tid":2311121,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:49:12.000Z","msg":"聽吓先，之前都講唔準大陸收購機械人公司，最後咪又係賣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"成間野總辭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}